Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I got here\Nas soon as I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but Friendship Ambassador is\Na full-time job these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Making peace between\NAbyssinians
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Diamond Dogs\Nhas {\i1}not{\i0} been easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I picked\Nyou for the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad\Nyou could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I took over\NCelestia's School,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,my focus has been\Non teaching magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it seems my\Ntop student has missed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the most important\Nlesson of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say it'll be good\Nto have my Royal Advisor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and Friendship\NAmbassador by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gallus: Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Send her in, Gallus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.49,0:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Luster, I may be the\Nruler of Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm still just\Nyour teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've been wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:01:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've enjoyed every moment\Nat the School of Magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but.. I'm just not sure it's\Nthe right place for {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I could spend WEEKS in the\Nlibrary doing research.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that.. there's a lot\Nof focus on making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's your problem, you've\Ncome to the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just it. I\Ndon't want to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you'd rather leave
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the School of Magic\Nthan make friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.42,0:01:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping to set up an\Nindependent course of study.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to accomplish as\Nmuch as you have someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be hard to do\Nthat without friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship looks like\Nmore of a distraction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,than anything else and\Nultimately a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you and your friends\Naccomplished a lot together,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.81,0:01:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but that was SO\Nlong ago and,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as I can see, you\Nrule by yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... hello? Royal\NAdvisor right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...And I don't think there's\Nanything wrong with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I think\Nit's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, if friendships\Nultimately fade,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,why even make them\Nin the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, Luster\NDawn? You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [dramatic sting] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship is more\Ntrouble than it's worth!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS is your top\Nstudent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendships take work,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no\Nguarantee they'll last.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be complicated.\NThey can be messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And they never go\Nthe way you plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship is a hard\Nthing to navigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the first\Ntime I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it might not last forever..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight? Uh... I'm pretty\Nsure that's everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing a\Nfinal check, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But we {\i1}did{\i0} a final\Ncheck. Of every room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,See? An issue of Power Ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, aren't you glad\Nwe triple checked?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but I already\Nread this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to take\Nit to Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. You love Power\NPonies! We're taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [rushing music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Twilight, we don't\Nhave to bring the comic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure how much\Nlonger I'll collect 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot is changing and\NI.. am getting older!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because things change
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean you leave\Neverything you love behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not still worried about\Nruling Equestria are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I know it took some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never been more ready\Nfor anything in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because I'm ready to sit\Non the throne in Canterlot
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean I'm ready\Nto leave Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were all fighting\Nto save Equestria from
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tirek, Chrysalis,\Nand Cozy Glow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too busy to\Nthink about it, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it's all happening at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The coronation, moving,\Nleaving our friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd all be\Nruling Equestria {\i1}together{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we will, but\Nit won't be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They all have lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're moving away\Nand they're not
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't help but feel like\Nwe're leaving them behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we all..\Njust drift apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I hadn't thought\Nabout it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they're\Nfeeling the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Spike. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes talking to a good\Nfriend is all it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're not worried about\Nhow things might change
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with me living in Canterlot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:04:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Change is natural,\Nlike the seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's.. just life on\Nthe farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhoo, I really need\Nto get all these boxes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,packed and sorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot more\Nwork now that the folks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond Equestria are coming\Nto the coronation too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Worried? Pfft! No way.\NUnless you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the coronation,\Nbecause then yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, the\Ncakes are handled,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's the whole rest of\Nthe party to stay on top of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And honestly, I'm\Nnot convinced
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gummy {\i1}really{\i0} took\Ncare of the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about AFTER\Nthe coronation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think things\Nare going to be... different?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since I'll be in charge\Nof all the Canterlot galas
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,from now on, I'll have\Nto go there a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess that's different,\Nbut I don't think I mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Of course not..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful work, everyone!\NWe couldn't be more ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Josephine, if you and the\Nrest of the doves leave now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we should all arrive in\NCanterlot at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eloise and Hubert,\Nyou should go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's a long\Nway, but don't worry;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring plenty of snacks\Nto restore your energy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,before we perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else gets to ride,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,since the trip's too much\Nfor your little wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We need everyone in tip-top\Nshape for the coronation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we got the chance\Nfor one last rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's so excited, but\NI can't imagine anypony's
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,more excited than you! Moving\Nto Canterlot. Being crowned...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of a single\Nbad thing about any of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[weakly] Heh-heh.\NYeah. Me, neither..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash:\NIn...3...2...1...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [heroic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Rainbow Dash, I know\Nthis is important to you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and we all want the\Nroutine to be special,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but are you sure it needs\Nto be this complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! And I know\Nwe can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Twilight. I\Ndon't have time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a LOT more work\Nto do before the coronation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, change is an\Nintegral part of fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself am considering\Nopening boutiques
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for non-ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Things must evolve or they\Nbecome {\i1}stale{\i0}. For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just struck with\Na sudden inspiration
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to change my design\Nfor your gown
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,by including the webs\Nof these star spiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They glow for a short\Nwhile after they're spun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't have much\Ntime to weave the sash,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but the effect will be\Ndazzling. You see, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Change can be fabulous\Nif you embrace it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight is supposed\Nto come over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a little something\Nwe wanted to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,before we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? I think\Nyou're right, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I SHOULD take my\Ncomics to Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave the\NPower Ponies behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the Power\NPonies care, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like all of\Nour friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Twilight.\NAre you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We all wanted to see you off,\Nbut there's still a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't {\i1}you{\i0} coming\Non the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go with Big Mac so we\Ncan go over our packing list
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,or we won't know who\Ngets what deliveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna meet\Nthe Wonderbolts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can go over the\Nroutine one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with Gummy.\NHe SAID he knows
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,when the fireworks\Ndisplay should start,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but does anypony\Nreally believe that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I still need to pick up\Nfood for the swans and doves
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,who flew ahead to Canterlot.\NIf I don't get them fed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll be too\Npooped to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be living\Nin Canterlot alone..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well take\Nthe train alone too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye! I guess..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you won't be\Ntraveling alone, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have just enough\Ntime on the train
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to weave the star spider\Nsash for your gown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But we should leave now.\NThere's no time to dawdle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want the\Ncoronation to be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all so worried about\Nmaking my coronation perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm leaving Ponyville\Nand none of you even CARE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. You moved away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends didn't\Ncare and that was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we care that\Nyou're moving, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nyou think we don't..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What could possibly\Nmake you think {\i1}that{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to talk to you all\Nabout how I was feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but you seemed more worried\Nabout what you had to do
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,for the coronation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it gave us\Nsomething else to focus on..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were worried\Nabout everything changin'..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I thought if I made it\Nseem like everything was OK,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to\Nmake you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, {\i1}I{\i0} wouldn't\Nfeel so terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I moved\Nto Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really know\Nwhat friendship WAS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all taught\Nme so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it\Nall might be ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I imagine the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,all I can think about is\Nthat we won't be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm literally moving away\Nfrom you and it's terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rattled to the core!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say {\i1}scared{\i0}..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. just because I {\i1}won't{\i0} say it\Ndoesn't mean I don't feel it..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing] I'm going\Nto miss you SO MUCH!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't stop\Nthinking about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,how much things are\Ngoing to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What-what if we\Ndon't see each other!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we don't\Ntalk as much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we don't\Nstay friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's weird, but knowing\Nyou're all are as upset as I am
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,actually makes me less worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice, but you\Nshould be more worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,about missing the\Ntrain to Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm so late! I actually\Nthought I'd missed you-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. We missed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. We're on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything should\Nbe fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd worked out exactly\Nhow much time I needed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to weave my star spider\Nsash, and now I'm behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Big Mac\Ncan figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,who gets what\Ndeliveries on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume these contain the\NFINEST sparkling apple juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the Sweet Apple\NAcres applesauce
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for my coronation parfait!\NThis {\i1}is{\i0} the applesauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Eeyup?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the snacks the\Ndoves and swans will need
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to perform after\Ntheir long flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better find the food car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I need to meet\Nthe Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the coronation team!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.. they waited, but\Nwhen you didn't show,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,they thought you musta meant\Nto meet outside of Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing\NI'm worried about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is Gummy handling the\Nfireworks display.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[uncertain] ...but\NI'm sure it's fine! [nervous laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it could always be worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, Twilight,\Nare you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends and I had a\Nfew hiccups on the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but everything's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We really are both\Njust so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need a moment,\Nthat's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It is your coronation..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [trumpet fanfare] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it would be nice to\Nget started. Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity: NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't possibly be crowned\Nwithout her coronation gown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia: Citizens of\NEquestria and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister and I have ruled\Nthis land for quite some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but even we know that change\Neventually comes to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And though we know it can be\Nunsettling, it's as natural
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,as the rising and setting\Nof the sun and the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of which my sister\Nand I feel confident
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving in the hooves of the\Npony who-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You look amazing.\NOh! I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia: And so\Nwithout further ado,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I give you the new\Nruler of Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [musical flourish] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Crowd: Ooooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Twilight..?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. I know these aren't\Nthe snacks I promised,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's all I could find.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Dash or no Dash,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight's about to get that\Ncrown. Wonderbolts, roll out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ [majestic music] ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Luster: OK. I get it now..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your coronation\Nwas such a disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that you and your friends\Nnever really recovered
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why you\Nall drifted apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're HALF right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So.. the coronation\N{\i1}wasn't{\i0} a disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and your friendships just\Nfaded away over time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not {\i1}exactly{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late, but it is\NSO hard to find a sitter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with a sense of humor\Nfor Li'l Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I would\Nhave been here sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but you would not believe\Nhow busy Yakyakistan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could get\Nto places on time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if you let me do\Nsome of the chores
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of always doing\Neverything yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I would if you\Ndid them the right way..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh heh, sorry. We're not\Nthe last ones, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord's headed to\Nan O&O convention
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or he'd be joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just assumed that\Nsince you aren't together
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That we aren't friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the\Npoint of my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true my coronation\Nwas a disaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least the\Ncoronation is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about to\Nsay the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know maybe it wasn't the\Ncoronation you planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's good to see\Nall of you laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to give this to you\Nbefore you left Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but things got a little hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're moving away,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we thought if you missed\Nany of us, or Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Awww!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a book of memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And we all chipped in some.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much\Nthings change,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll always have\Nthis to look back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it. Thank you\NSO much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want\Nto only look back..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, the coronation\Nwasn't perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our relationships\Nthat really count
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have to maintain them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that we're\Nliving in different places,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly sure how..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. I suggest we\Nmeet once a moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, my first royal\Ndecree as ruler of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is to establish this\NCouncil of Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia: And what a\Nwonderful decree it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We always knew that whatever\Nadversity you faced, you and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,your friends would find your\Nway through it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We know Equestria is in the\Nperfect hooves with you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,AND your friends\Nlooking out for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And while we'll always\Nbe here if you need us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it's time for us\Nto be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving..?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We hope you'll come and\Nvisit us in Silver Shoals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it's time for\Nyou to rule on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all MORE than capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. For everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even though\Neverything changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and you moved away\Nfrom your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't grow apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And {\i1}THIS{\i0} is the\NCouncil of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're\Nall doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Duh. This time every moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. What she means is, this is how\Nwe've been ruling together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And how we've continued\Nto face every problem
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and threat to Equestria\Nover the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But mostly, it's how\Nwe keep in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how busy life gets!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes friendships\Ncan be hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and it takes work\Nto maintain them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but without friends,\Nthings can be a lot harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought\Nabout friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,being something to work\Nat.. and I don't mind work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess if they don't\Nhave to fade away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe making friends isn't\Nthe waste of time I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. I've been so\Nfocused on my studies,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know\Nwhere to start.
